<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10170989>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Paranesotanais incisus sp. nov. specimens (ethanol-preserved), photo by You-Wei Tzeng. Paratype (NMNS8568- 11), female: A, dorsal view. Allotype (NMNS8568-06), male: B, dorsal view; C, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10170989/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10170993>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Paranesotanais incisus sp. nov. Holotype (NMNS8568-05), female: A, body dorsal view; C, right antennule; E, right antenna (outer view); G, labrum. Allotype (NMNS8568-06), male: B, body dorsal view; D, right antennule; F, right antenna (outer view)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10170993/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10170995>
    dc:description "FIGURE 12. Paranesotanais incisus sp. nov. Holotype (NMNS8568-05), female: A, left mandible; B, right mandible; C, right mandible incisor; D, labium; E, maxillule endite; F, maxilliped; G, maxilliped endite; I, right cheliped; J, right cheliped propodus and dactylus inner view. Allotype (NMNS8568-06), male: H, maxilliped." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10170995/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10170997>
    dc:description "FIGURE 13. Paranesotanais incisus sp. nov. Holotype (NMNS8568-05), female:A–B, right pereopods 1–2; C, left pereopod-3; D, right pereopod-4; E–F, left pereopods 5–6; G, right pleopod-1 (all setae circumplumose, setules omitted); H, right uropod." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10170997/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10170999>
    dc:description "FIGURE 14. Paranesotanais incisus sp. nov. Allotype (NMNS8568-06), male: A, right cheliped; B, right cheliped ventral view; C–H, right pereopods 1–6." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10170999/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

